{"ja511:0.1":"Jataka ","ja511:0.2":"Timsanipata ","ja511:0.3":"Kimchandavagga ","ja511:0.4":"1. Kimchandajataka ","ja511:1.1":"“Kimchando kimadhippayo, ","ja511:1.2":"eko sammasi ghammani; ","ja511:1.3":"Kim patthayano kim esam, ","ja511:1.4":"kena atthena brahmana”. ","ja511:2.1":"“Yatha maha varidharo, ","ja511:2.2":"kumbho suparinahava; ","ja511:2.3":"Tathupamam ambapakkam, ","ja511:2.4":"vannagandharasuttamam. ","ja511:3.1":"Tam vuyhamanam sotena, ","ja511:3.2":"disvanamalamajjhime; ","ja511:3.3":"Panihi nam gahetvana, ","ja511:3.4":"agyayatanamaharim. ","ja511:4.1":"Tato kadalipattesu, ","ja511:4.2":"nikkhipitva sayam aham; ","ja511:4.3":"Satthena nam vikappetva, ","ja511:4.4":"khuppipasam ahasi me. ","ja511:5.1":"Soham apetadaratho, ","ja511:5.2":"Byantibhuto dukhakkhamo; ","ja511:5.3":"Assadam nadhigacchami, ","ja511:5.4":"Phalesvannesu kesuci. ","ja511:6.1":"Sosetva nuna maranam, ","ja511:6.2":"tam mamam avahissati; ","ja511:6.3":"Ambam yassa phalam sadu, ","ja511:6.4":"madhuraggam manoramam; ","ja511:6.5":"Yamuddharim vuyhamanam, ","ja511:6.6":"udadhisma mahannave. ","ja511:7.1":"Akkhatam te maya sabbam, ","ja511:7.2":"yasma upavasamaham; ","ja511:7.3":"Rammam pati nisinnosmi, ","ja511:7.4":"puthulomayuta puthu. ","ja511:8.1":"Tvanca kho meva akkhahi, ","ja511:8.2":"attanamapalayini; ","ja511:8.3":"Ka va tvamasi kalyani, ","ja511:8.4":"kissa va tvam sumajjhime. ","ja511:9.1":"Ruppapattapalimatthiva, ","ja511:9.2":"byagghiva girisanuja; ","ja511:9.3":"Ya santi nariyo devesu, ","ja511:9.4":"devanam paricarika. ","ja511:10.1":"Ya ca manussalokasmim, ","ja511:10.2":"Rupenanvagatitthiyo; ","ja511:10.3":"Rupena te sadisi natthi, ","ja511:10.4":"Devesu gandhabbamanussaloke; ","ja511:10.5":"Putthasi me carupubbangi, ","ja511:10.6":"Bruhi namanca bandhave”. ","ja511:11.1":"“Yam tvam pati nisinnosi, ","ja511:11.2":"rammam brahmana kosikim; ","ja511:11.3":"Saham bhusalayavuttha, ","ja511:11.4":"varavarivahoghasa. ","ja511:12.1":"Nanadumaganakinna, ","ja511:12.2":"bahuka girikandara; ","ja511:12.3":"Mameva pamukha honti, ","ja511:12.4":"abhisandanti pavuse. ","ja511:13.1":"Atho bahu vanatoda, ","ja511:13.2":"nilavarivahindhara; ","ja511:13.3":"Bahuka nagavittoda, ","ja511:13.4":"abhisandanti varina. ","ja511:14.1":"Ta ambajambulabuja, ","ja511:14.2":"nipa tala cudumbara; ","ja511:14.3":"Bahuni phalajatani, ","ja511:14.4":"avahanti abhinhaso. ","ja511:15.1":"Yam kinci ubhato tire, ","ja511:15.2":"phalam patati ambuni; ","ja511:15.3":"Asamsayam tam sotassa, ","ja511:15.4":"phalam hoti vasanugam. ","ja511:16.1":"Etadannaya medhavi, ","ja511:16.2":"puthupanna sunohi me; ","ja511:16.3":"Ma rocaya mabhisangam, ","ja511:16.4":"patisedha janadhipa. ","ja511:17.1":"Na vaham vaddhavam manne, ","ja511:17.2":"Yam tvam ratthabhivaddhana; ","ja511:17.3":"Aceyyamano rajisi, ","ja511:17.4":"Maranam abhikankhasi. ","ja511:18.1":"Tassa jananti pitaro, ","ja511:18.2":"gandhabba ca sadevaka; ","ja511:18.3":"Ye capi isayo loke, ","ja511:18.4":"sannatatta tapassino; ","ja511:18.5":"Asamsayam tepi jananti, ","ja511:18.6":"patthabhuta yasassino”. ","ja511:19.1":"“Evam viditva vidu sabbadhammam, ","ja511:19.2":"Viddhamsanam cavanam jivitassa; ","ja511:19.3":"Na ciyati tassa narassa papam, ","ja511:19.4":"Sace na ceteti vadhaya tassa. ","ja511:20.1":"Isipugasamannate, ","ja511:20.2":"evam lokya vidita sati; ","ja511:20.3":"Anariyaparisambhase, ","ja511:20.4":"papakammam jigisasi. ","ja511:21.1":"Sace aham marissami, ","ja511:21.2":"tire te puthusussoni; ","ja511:21.3":"Asamsayam tam asiloko, ","ja511:21.4":"mayi pete agamissati. ","ja511:22.1":"Tasma hi papakam kammam, ","ja511:22.2":"rakkhasseva sumajjhime; ","ja511:22.3":"Ma tam sabbo jano paccha, ","ja511:22.4":"pakutthayi mayi mate”. ","ja511:23.1":"“Annatametam avisayhasahi, ","ja511:23.2":"Attanamambanca dadami te tam; ","ja511:23.3":"So duccaje kamagune pahaya, ","ja511:23.4":"Santinca dhammanca adhitthitosi. ","ja511:24.1":"Yo hitva pubbasannogam, ","ja511:24.2":"paccha samyojane thito; ","ja511:24.3":"Adhammanceva carati, ","ja511:24.4":"papancassa pavaddhati. ","ja511:25.1":"Ehi tam papayissami, ","ja511:25.2":"kamam appossuko bhava; ","ja511:25.3":"Upanayami sitasmim, ","ja511:25.4":"viharahi anussuko. ","ja511:26.1":"Tam puppharasamattebhi, ","ja511:26.2":"vakkangehi arindama; ","ja511:26.3":"Konca mayura diviya, ","ja511:26.4":"kolatthimadhusalika; ","ja511:26.5":"Kujita hamsapugehi, ","ja511:26.6":"kokilettha pabodhare. ","ja511:27.1":"Ambettha vippasakhagga, ","ja511:27.2":"palalakhalasannibha; ","ja511:27.3":"Kosambasalala nipa, ","ja511:27.4":"pakkatalavilambino”. ","ja511:28.1":"“Mali tiriti kayuri, ","ja511:28.2":"angadi candanussado; ","ja511:28.3":"Rattim tvam paricaresi, ","ja511:28.4":"diva vedesi vedanam. ","ja511:29.1":"Solasitthisahassani, ","ja511:29.2":"ya tema paricarika; ","ja511:29.3":"Evam mahanubhavosi, ","ja511:29.4":"abbhuto lomahamsano. ","ja511:30.1":"Kim kammamakari pubbe, ","ja511:30.2":"papam attadukhavaham; ","ja511:30.3":"Yam karitva manussesu, ","ja511:30.4":"pitthimamsani khadasi”. ","ja511:31.1":"“Ajjhenani patiggayha, ","ja511:31.2":"kamesu gadhito aham; ","ja511:31.3":"Acarim dighamaddhanam, ","ja511:31.4":"paresam ahitayaham. ","ja511:32.1":"Yo pitthimamsiko hoti, ","ja511:32.2":"evam ukkacca khadati; ","ja511:32.3":"Yathaham ajja khadami, ","ja511:32.4":"pitthimamsani attano”ti. ","ja511:33.1":"Kimchandajatakam pathamam. "}